''' Bugwisan''' is a mountain of [[Jeollabuk-do]], western [[South Korea]]. It has an altitude of 806 metres.<ref>{{cite book| last=An Gyeong-ho | year=2007| title=<U+D55C><U+AD6D> 300 <U+BA85><U+C0B0> (300 Korean Mountains) |location=Seoul|publisher=<U+AE4A><U+C740><U+C194> (Gipeunsol)|isbn=978-89-89917-21-2}}</ref>

